<doc id="983396" wikidata="Q3286245" url="?curid=983396" title="Nu Thang">
<text>Nu Thang is the second studio album from DC Talk, which was released in 1990. It was certified Gold by RIAA. Almost two decades later, the single &quot;Nu Thang&quot; and its YouTube video gained more recognition after a viral video was put up known as &quot;The Nu Thang Kid&quot;. It is a video of a boy from the 1990s rapping &quot;Nu Thang&quot;, and the video was used on an episode of Equals Three.

